{"id":"172338516139198_957279237645118","from":{"name":"Mohammad Tayseer","id":"10154965677956341"},"message":"MicroPython is a special version of Python 3 which can run on a microcontroller (Pyboard). The European Space Agency is funding it.\n\nOn this attached link, you can see it in action & even write code to run on it :)\n\nESA is funding MicroPython\nhttp://forum.micropython.org/viewtopic.php?t=744","story":"Mohammad Tayseer shared a link to the group: Egyptian Geeks.","story_tags":{"0":[{"id":"10154965677956341","name":"Mohammad Tayseer","type":"user","offset":0,"length":16}],"45":[{"id":"172338516139198","name":"Egyptian Geeks","type":"group","offset":45,"length":14}]},"link":"http://micropython.org/live/","name":"MicroPython - Python for microcontrollers","caption":"micropython.org","description":"MicroPython - Python for microcontrollers","icon":"https://www.facebook.com/images/icons/post.gif","actions":[{"name":"Comment","link":"https://www.facebook.com/172338516139198/posts/957279237645118"},{"name":"Like","link":"https://www.facebook.com/172338516139198/posts/957279237645118"},{"name":"Report Post to Admin","link":"https://www.facebook.com/groups/egyptian.geeks/members/"}],"privacy":{"value":"","description":"","friends":"","allow":"","deny":""},"type":"link","status_type":"shared_story","created_time":"2015-06-11T18:56:42+0000","updated_time":"2015-06-12T10:01:31+0000","is_hidden":false,"is_expired":false,"likes":{"data":[{"id":"10154277762775373","name":"Hussein Eldabaa"},{"id":"10212281470221629","name":"Mohamed Ali Abuelwafa"},{"id":"10212736613196934","name":"Mohamed Elnagar"},{"id":"10158483817400314","name":"Mohamed Elsherif"},{"id":"10155141160589222","name":"Mohamed Mahmoud Abdallah"},{"id":"10154871355735944","name":"Tarek Amr"},{"id":"10212348961303729","name":"Abdulaziz Alaa"},{"id":"770108719813462","name":"Ali Zawahry"},{"id":"10154202258522653","name":"Ahmed E. Naiem"},{"id":"1223432184393227","name":"Mohamed Badawi"},{"id":"1021278279723